{"tid":2460986,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京多名受訪市民稱會抵制H&M產品","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:30:57.000Z","uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7fa70dce2b24ce0f7cae9e0245b0a8a6eba986b","tid":2460986,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:09:24.000Z","msg":"內地多個官方媒體批評瑞典服裝品牌H&amp;M有關沒有購買新疆棉花產品的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，多名受訪的市民均表明，會抵制H&amp;M的產品。有市民認為，想賺中國人的錢，就要尊重中國人。對於新彊問題，他指外國需要調查實際情況才發言。<br />\n<br />\n另一名市民表示，新彊是棉花最好的出產地，認為比H&amp;M等外來快銷品牌的衣服材質為高。她認為，中國人要自強，不在意外來品牌是否扺制中國好的原材料，中國亦有足夠人口，有龐大消費市場支持新彊棉。<br />\n<br />\n至於在北京朝陽區的H&amp;M分店，仍有市民內進購物。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582523-20210325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582523-20210325.htm&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxiDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=3d125042\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582523-20210325.htm&h=8db1b578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582523-20210325.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4c38acd54acaac1fd513ff4c884ce71ca9886cde","tid":2460986,"uid":29947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"n年前舊話唔去香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到好厭"},{"pid":"419bcb331c5daa9f77036b83fb80ec1a8a623585","tid":2460986,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"我很幸福 我很幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會抵制 我會抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d482f639a33ccc5b2b8859ce616a0ba04f8f87b","tid":2460986,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}